ng was a real surprise, a shock. All I ever knew was the fact that his plane had exploded in mid-air over those islands.'' The family is trying to get <PERSON> Marsman </PERSON>'s remains, buried in a war cemetery in <LOCATION> Indonesia </LOCATION>, returned to <LOCATION> Mississippi </LOCATION> and buried in a small cemetery for Dutch pilots who died in training. `` He wanted to be buried back here if anything happened to him,'' said Mrs. <PERSON> Baker </PERSON>. `` And it would mean a lot for <PERSON> Larry </PERSON>.'' However, efforts to secure help from the American and Dutch governments to exhume the body have n't been successful so far. `` The <LOCATION> United </LOCATION> <LOCATION> States </LOCATION> trained him and he fought for freedom,'' <PERSON> Larry </PERSON> <PERSON> Marsman </PERSON> said. `` He wanted to be buried here because he felt his family was here. I know this sounds silly, but I think that's why this ring has worked its way back through all these years He's telling me to do something and I pray that I can.
